Class LeafNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • decoder.AbstractNode
      • decoder.LeafNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TreeNode

    public class LeafNode
extends AbstractNode
    A LeafNode class that represents a node at the last level or the bottom level. It has all operations depicted by the TreeNode interface.
